Invocation Name: murphy's bylaws
des:
Had a rough day? You may not have been clued in to the way life really works. 

But don't worry! In just a few minutes with this new Alexa skill, you will arm yourself with the witty observations of Mr. Murphy, and be ready for the next curve ball life throws at you. 

There are over 100+ observations on life, in the areas of Love, Education, and Work, and general categories. And we're continuing to add other areas, so check back often for new updates. 

How many times have these happened to you? Which one is your favorite? Leave a review and let us know!
